Title: Aversion to Harmful Actions in Moral Choice Behaviour
Description: Psychological study using an experimental economic approach to observe how self and other regarding outcome incentives affect harm aversion in real moral choice behaviour.
Contributors: Pri Perera, Elliot  Ludvig, Emina Canic
Tags: 

Aversion to Harmful Actions in Moral Choice Behaviour
Psychological study using an experimental economic approach to observe how self and other regarding outcome incentives affect harm aversion in real moral choice behaviour.
